---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    I defended my PhD at <a class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 underline" href="https://www.cmu.edu/dietrich/psychology/caoslab/">Prof. Brad Mahon's lab</a> at the University of Rochester in New York in 2018, where I studied how human represent object knowledge with machine learning techniques, and gained a wealth of experience designing and programming computer-based
    tests with Python and Matlab. </br> Following that I was a postdoctoral research scientist in <a class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 underline" href="https://www.cogtlab.com/">Prof. Vankee Lin's lab</a>, where I conducted research on applying machine learning to brain data in Alzheimer's disease
    field.</br> In July 2023, I joined <a class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 underline" href="https://www.lucidmotors.com/">Lucid Motors</a>  as a Frontend Developer, eager to apply my combined skills and knowledge in software development, machine learning, and cognitive research. While my position primarily focuses on the frontend, I am equally intrigued by the challenges and complexities of the backend. I'm enthusiastic about contributing to the design and development of innovative solutions that can enhance people's lives.</br>
